dc_title_s: Port Facilities at Port of New York, Arthur Kill
dc_description_s: Map 1: The main purpose of the map is to show the Port Facilities of the Port of New York on the Arthur Kill; however, the map expands to show more of the river including tributaries, bridges and some streets.|Map 2: The main purpose of the map is to show the Philadelphia & Reading R.R. Coal Terminal on the Arthur Kill; however, the map expands to show more of the river including tributaries.
